@startuml
' Embedded standalone style block (replicated per file; standalone)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor White
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam nodesep 50
skinparam ranksep 60
skinparam padding 3
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

left to right direction

actor "Administrador\n(rol admin)" as Admin
actor "Personal Logistico\n(rol staff, lectura)" as Staff
boundary "Angular Admin\n(products / Apollo)" as Boundary
control "Catalog resolvers\n(mutations.go)" as Resolvers
control "CatalogService\n(catalog_service.go)" as Service
entity "Product / ProductVariant\n(catalog.go)" as Entity
database "NeonDB\n(PostgreSQL)" as DB
control "Subsistema Documental\n(MS3 documentos)" as MS3

Admin --> Boundary : 1: createProduct / updateProduct /\ncreateVariant / activate / deactivate
Staff --> Boundary : 1b: query products (lectura)
Boundary --> Resolvers : 2: mutation / query (POST /graphql)
Resolvers --> Resolvers : 3: requireAdmin / requireAuth (rol JWT)
Resolvers --> MS3 : 4: replaceProductImage (document id imagen)
MS3 --> Resolvers : 5: document id confirmado
Resolvers --> Service : 6: CreateProduct / CreateVariant (input validado)
Service --> Entity : 7: construir / modificar Product / Variant
Entity --> DB : 8: INSERT / UPDATE / SELECT products, product_variants
DB --> Entity : 9: filas persistidas / leidas
Entity --> Resolvers : 10: Product / Variant
Resolvers --> Boundary : 11: Product / Variant actualizado o listado
Boundary --> Admin : 12: refrescar catalogo
@enduml
